svg/svg.svg#menu"></use></svg></div><div class="custom-padding slide-content"><ul class="checkbox-list" data-section="heating"><li class="active" data="all"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> ALL <b>(1508)</b></label></li><li class="" data="air-conditioning"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Air Conditioning <b>(953)</b></label></li><li class="" data="central-heating"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Central Heating <b>(16)</b></label></li><li class="" data="fan-coil"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Fan Coil <b>(27)</b></label></li><li class="" data="gas-combi"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Gas Combi <b>(127)</b></label></li><li class="" data="heat-share-meter"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Heat Share Meter <b>(5)</b></label></li><li class="" data="solar-energy"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Solar Energy <b>(32)</b></label></li><li class="" data="stove"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Stove <b>(7)</b></label></li><li class="" data="underfloor-cooling"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Underfloor Cooling <b>(18)</b></label></li><li class="" data="underfloor-heating"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> Underfloor Heating <b>(323)</b></label></li></ul></div></div><div class="option"><div class="title"> ORIENTATION FEATURES <svg><use xlink:href="/images/svg/svg.svg#menu"></use></svg></div><div class="custom-padding slide-content"><ul class="checkbox-list" data-section="orientation"><li class="active" data="all"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> ALL <b>(4675)</b></label></li><li class="" data="west"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> West <b>(703)</b></label></li><li class="" data="east"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> East <b>(724)</b></label></li><li class="" data="north"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> North <b>(640)</b></label></li><li class="" data="south"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> South <b>(873)</b></label></li><li class="" data="north-west"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> North-West <b>(335)</b></label></li><li class="" data="north-east"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> North-East <b>(318)</b></label></li><li class="" data="south-west"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> South-West <b>(558)</b></label></li><li class="" data="south-east"><label><span class="checkbox"></span> South-East <b>(524)</b></label></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="filter-buttons"><div class="row"><div class="view-results btn"> VIEW RESULTS </div><div class="reset-filter btn" data-url="/real-estate/turkey"> CLEAR ALL </div></div></div></div><div class="right-block"><article class="top-side landing-container"><h1>Real Estate for Sale in Turkey | Property in Turkey</h1><section class="content"><div class="lpmetin"><p>Antalya Homes ® offers a wide variety of properties for sale in Turkey. Check out our properties for sale in the best places to live in Turkey.</p><p>Located at the intersection of Europe and Asia continents, Anatolia has been a matter of debate throughout history. Being surrounded by the Aegean Sea, the Black Sea, and the Mediterranean Sea and being home to numerous natural wonders on top of its strategic location has made Anatolia the desired land for many civilizations.</p><p>Nowadays Turkey, being established in Anatolia, is a popular place among foreigners for both visiting on their holidays and for settling permanently as well owing to its picturesque beauties and rich cultural heritage.</p><p>As a result, the number of people who buy property in Turkey to live in and the number of people who are investing in Turkish properties for sale to gain profit increased rapidly. Here are just a few of the reasons why.</p><h2>Why Invest in Real Estate in Turkey?</h2><p><img alt="Property for Sale in Turkey | Real Estate in Turkey" class="lazyload full" src="/images/bos.jpg" data-src="https://tekce.net/files/upload/images/beach-olympos-turkey-rs.jpg" style="float:left; height:247px; margin:10px; width:330px" title="Property for Sale in Turkey | Real Estate in Turkey" /></p><p>Buying real estate for sale in Turkey is not only a great choice for a residence but a very good investment as well. First of all, property prices in Turkey are quite low compared to many other countries with similar features and lifestyles. There is a wide range of cheap properties in Turkey from compact but new-build apartments to resale investment properties.</p><p>Secondly, the advantageous real estate market makes investing in a <a href="https://antalyahomes.com/commercial/turkey" target="_self">commercial property in Turkey</a> such as hotels, business centers, and offices, or buying a residence such as apartments, quite an attractive and profitable investment option.</p><p>Thirdly, the Turkish real estate market has a fast-growing nature and the prices are expected to go up considerably due to the latest developments and high demand. Buying Turkey real estate for sale in the near future will ensure an excellent return on most investments within a few years..</p><p>Additionally, the costs of living are also pretty low in Turkey. As a result of these conditions, you can purchase property in Turkey that is equal to properties in Europe or even a better one for a great deal and lead a comfortable and posh life with less money.</p><p>The low costs of living, the profitable Turkey real estate market, decent living conditions, the healthy environment, and welcoming people can be sorted as a few reasons to live here.</p><p>Another beneficial point of purchasing real estate in Turkey is that you can also apply for Turkish citizenship. Buying property in Turkey for citizenship is probably the easiest way to acquire Turkish citizenship. When the property you bought complies with the terms and conditions, there will be no hampers on the road that takes you to obtain Turkish citizenship.</p><h3>Buying a Property for Sale in Turkey: What to Purchase?</h3><p>The real estate market in Turkey is a rapidly growing business line because of the latest developments in construction technologies and the high demand. While taking a look at Turkish real estate websites, you may feel a bit dizzy because of the vast amount of properties.</p><p>The wide range of property options and different prices on different websites may be confusing for foreign investors. Most of them may not be appealing to you but that's okay, no reason to feel lost. With professional guidance, choosing the right property is as easy as pie.</p><p>When it comes to property investment, trust is the most important factor. Working with a professional and well-established real estate company plays an important role in choosing the best option for you, your family, or your business.</p><p>You will be able to find the best property suitable to your needs and match up your expectations easily when you work with expert real estate agents. Let's check out what are the property types and find the Turkey property for sale that is most convenient for you:</p><p><strong>Residences</strong></p><p><img alt="Property for Sale in Turkey | Real Estate in Turkey" class="lazyload full" src="/images/bos.jpg" data-src="https://tekce.net/files/upload/images/properties-for-sale-in-turkey.jpg" style="float:right; height:360px; margin:5px; width:360px" title="Property for Sale in Turkey | Real Estate in Turkey" /></p><p>As a developed country, Turkey presents a wide variety of residences. It’s possible to find a residence for every lifestyle, so it won’t be hard to find a suitable one for yourself. However, you need to take the status of the property into account when buying a residence in Turkey.</p><p>When it comes to buying a house or an apartment, the status of the property is a significant detail. For instance, the off-plan and under-construction projects draw attention with their advantageous prices. But, you need to note that you’ll have to wait until the construction is over to move in.</p><p>Even so, newly built apartments are a great choice for <a href="https://antalyahomes.com/apartments/turkey?search&tags=luxury" target="_self">buying luxury apartments in Turkey</a> because they are mostly designed with modern features to meet the conditions of contemporary lifestyle. Istanbul, Antalya, and Bodrum are some of the most popular places where you can find luxurious apartments.</p><p>If you want to provide more outdoor and indoor spaces for your loved ones as well as a posh lifestyle, you can look for detached <a href="https://antalyahomes.com/houses/turkey" target="_self">houses for sale in Turkey</a> with a garden and a terrace. This way you will have ample social areas and living spaces for each member of your family. Fethiye, Milas, and Alanya are the places to look for villas in addition to Istanbul, Antalya, and Bodrum.</p><p>If you want to buy a cheap but comfortable residence to live in, there are many luxurious new-build residential projects in Istanbul and Antalya. These projects usually feature budget-friendly compact apartments as well. However, if what you are looking for is a cheap property to make an investment in, you can easily find cheap resale properties anywhere in Turkey.</p><p>Turkey presents suitable property options for people who are in search of a rural lifestyle or for people who just want to lead a peaceful life in a more tranquil place. Some districts of Trabzon, Bursa, Yalova, Kocaeli, and Balıkesir offer just about this type of lifestyle.</p><p><strong>Commercial Properties</strong></p><p>Are you looking for a commercial property for sale in Turkey to establish a new business or maybe planning to open a new branch of an existing one? Turkey is one of the best choices with a comprehensive business sector, especially in metropolitan cities such as Istanbul, the capital of Ankara, a worldwide known vacation spot of Bodrum, or the heart of the Mediterranean: Antalya.</p><p>In recent years, Alanya Turkey real estate has started to draw immense attention from foreign property buyers in addition to the ones in the above-mentioned places. As Alanya has become one of the top holiday destinations in Turkey, the investment value of commercial real estate in Alanya has increased greatly.</p><p>All cities in Turkey bear a high-profit potential when it comes to joining the world of trade, tourism, or retail. Its advantageous location on the major trade routes, a healthy environment filled with natural beauties and cultural heritage subjects, a wide range of entertainment centers, and a colorful lifestyle make Turkey a high-demanded country with nearly 50 million visitors per year. This status of the country creates a perfect environment for investors.</p><p><strong>Land</strong></p><p>There are multiple types of lands in Turkey such as agricultural lands suitable for farming, residential lands which are permitted for residential constructions, and commercial lands to build a commercial properties such as warehouses, factories, workshops, etc.</p><p>Depending on the purpose of the purchase, you can buy <a href="https://antalyahomes.com/land/turkey" target="_self">land for sale in Turkey</a> to build your own dream house, do agricultural activities, or build a commercial property to expand the necessary spaces for your business.</p><p>While the decent environment and convenient climate create the perfect environment for the rural lifestyle, Turkey's convenient soil texture creates the perfect opportunity for farming activities. Approximately 30,8% of lands in Turkey are reserved for agricultural activities and livestock businesses, hence you can find agricultural lands without any trouble. Antalya, Trabzon, Kocaeli, and Balıkesir are where you should look for agricultural lands.</p><p>On the other hand, construction-permitted lands present an opportunity to make a profitable investment on a much larger scale. As many people are competing with each other to buy property in Turkey Antalya, a residential or commercial project built on the construction-permitted lands in Antalya is bound to be a lucrative investment.</p><p>If you want to buy a property in Turkey but are unable to come at the moment due to your busy schedule, rest assured! We can follow up on the whole buying process in place and notify you at every stage through our TeleProperty ® service.</p><p>Our professional local real estate agents can handle the time-consuming procedures from opening a bank account to making utility subscriptions on your behalf with your power of attorney.</p></div></section></article><div class="bottom-side"><span class="page-title">Real Estate for Sale in Turkey | Property in Turkey</span><section class="showing-results"> Showing Results: <strong>1071</strong></section><section class="search-list-tabs"><ul><li class="active" data-section="list">Property Listings</li><li data-section="office">Visit Our Offices</li></ul></section><article class="search-list-container data-section" data-section="list"><ul class="filter-buttons"><li class="button"><svg class="filter-icon"><use xlink:href="/images/svg/svg.svg#filter-icon"></use></svg> FILTER <span>(1)</span></li><li class="select"><svg class="sort-icon"><use xlink:href="/images/svg/svg.svg#sort"></use></svg> SORT BY <ul class="ranking"><li class="active"><a href="#" data="numberH">Recently Added</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="priceH">Price: Highest First</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="priceL">Price: Lowest First</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="recommended">Recommended</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="sizeH">Size: Bigger First</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="sizeL">Size: Smaller First</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="visitedH">Most Visited</a></li></ul></li></ul><div class="desktop-filter-container"><ul class="suggested-filters"><li class="active"><a href="#" data="numberH">Recently Added</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="recommended">Recommended</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="priceH">Price: Highest First</a></li><li ><a href="#" data="priceL">Price: Lowest First</a></li></ul><div class="select"> OTHERS <u